{
  "description": "This space provides an overview of insured properties, including their locations, operational status, and key business classifications, enabling analysis of property distribution and characteristics across regions.\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- Analyze the geographic distribution of insured properties by country, region, locality, or postcode.\n- Assess operational status and business classification of insured properties.\n- Track changes to property records over time using version history.\n- Map property locations and perform spatial analyses, such as calculating distances or coverage areas.\n\n**Limitations:**\n- Does not include financial or claim-related data for insured properties.\n- Lacks detailed information on property size, construction details, or risk assessments.\n- Limited to point location data; does not provide full property boundaries.",
